{"tid":148543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"猶差得閒到幫有錢女搵狗","createTime":"2017-03-08T16:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T16:46:09.000Z","uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"037ff9b68fd1ed593d86f382cbc128e9feef051b","tid":148543,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:05:20.000Z","msg":"奧海城貴婦狗走失　58歲男帶回家飼養　涉盜狗被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/article/76638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F76638&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9ad1cf40\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/article/76638</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/459472/xlarge/336c934e9eacc75553ff0f37749d6981.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F459472%2Fxlarge%2F336c934e9eacc75553ff0f37749d6981.jpg&h=aff46e9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港不時發生犬隻走失事件，令狗主痛心萬分。今年1月，奧海城2期發生懷疑盜狗案，一隻3歲貴婦狗女被一名男子帶走，事隔2個月後，警方終透過天眼助狗主尋回愛犬，讓人狗兩團圓，並拘捕涉嫌盜狗的58歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n狗女散步時失走　男子帶走並寄養友人家中<br />\n<br />\n事發於今年1月19日，莫小姐（31歲）的傭人攜家中兩隻狗到奧海城二期散步時，3歲貴婦狗女Kelly突然走失，作為狗主的莫小姐心急如焚，借助網上群組及街招等不同方式尋犬，惟不得要領。莫於2月21日報警求助，警方翻查閉路電視，發現Kelly走失後被一名男子帶走，該名男子其後把Kelly寄養到其友人位於九龍城的家中。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後，於昨晚（7日）6時於九龍城區尋獲Kelly，其後於大角嘴區拘捕帶走Kelly的58歲姓馬男子，馬涉嫌盜取狗隻，目前獲准保釋候查。據了解，被捕人家中亦有養狗，於街上帶走Kelly後一直收留在家，沒有聯絡漁護署和警方，其後又把Kelly寄養到朋友的九龍城家中。莫小姐對尋回愛犬感到十分高興，慶幸Kelly沒有因此消瘦及變得怕人，並感謝警方協助。"},{"pid":"ab51264282698247801eddb7df649c3d7996e77d","tid":148543,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137379bb41fd3099d5129ea7faf422a83a6785ec","tid":148543,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709e0c47c5bebff8b1fe83598d247293f39cc451","tid":148543,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:26:27.000Z","msg":"奧海城先幫你搵昨,你試下海富苑?告能埋你阻差辦工"},{"pid":"38adbcae9af7bc710369acf5f3dd2985adff5a24","tid":148543,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奧海城先幫你搵昨,你試下海富苑?告能埋你阻差辦工</blockquote><br />\n阿叔執返去養都要拉<br />\n咁平時周圍捉貓個d貓義工點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81a64c25040aad4de383fc652e2edc6ac1478a6","tid":148543,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奧海城先幫你搵昨,你試下海富苑?告能埋你阻差辦工</blockquote><br />\n唔係奧海城點上到報？"},{"pid":"40cde71e6987b5a18a9dcaf6bb5f303fcfdf8f5a","tid":148543,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"又話隻狗走失<br />\n<br />\n但係又話人偷狗???"},{"pid":"5b4cd4f23e034126a74d1565131db47d341d2f70","tid":148543,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話隻狗走失<br />\n<br />\n但係又話人偷狗???</blockquote><br />\n阿叔執咗隻狗當拾遺不報"},{"pid":"ac2c3eaea5293c54134cfdca46a269c028b02995","tid":148543,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>奧海城先幫你搵昨,你試下海富苑?告能埋你阻差辦工</blockquote><br />\n唔係奧海城點上到報？</blockquote><br />\n一個奧海城<br />\n一個大角咀<br />\n<br />\n窮撚等坐監喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}